snippet.title: Dotto Botto - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
#Construct3 #indiegame #gamedevelopment
Dotto Botto is a platformer game developed in Construct 3
it's a classic super mario style 10 levels long platformer, with two endings.
I made all the code and the graphics assets for this one.

FREE on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pitigamedev.dottobotto

Available on itch.io https://pitigamedev.itch.io/dotto-botto

Music credit: https://twitter.com/TwistwonkaE

My Game Assets: https://www.gamedevmarket.net/member/Pierpaolo%20Tausani/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/pitigamedev
My Games: https://pitigamedev.itch.io/​​​​
ArtStation: https://www.artstation.com/pierpaolo87​​
BlenderArtist https://blenderartists.org/u/pierpaolo/activity/portfolio
